name: Dashboard Charts UI Kit
description:
45+ Dashboard and Charting elements with a easy edit global design system. Updated every 2 weeks with more amazing and interesting design elements. Comes with both Light mode and Dark mode. 

All the elements are easily editable, no hassle of frames and components only rectangles used. Very simple color and font only design system will get any beginner started.

Any requests and feedbacks will be thankfully accepted. Happy Designing!
